work.summary: Experienced in leading baristas during high-volume periods by delegating tasks effectively and coaching team members to maintain company standards. Creates a welcoming environment, resolves customer issues promptly, and ensures guests receive high-quality service and beverages. Skilled in overseeing daily store operations, including cash handling, safe counts, break coordination, inventory monitoring, and maintaining compliance with company policies.

Provide outstanding customer service by efficiently preparing handcrafted beverages while ensuring a positive customer experience. Thrive in high-volume environments by delivering prompt service and consistently meeting company quality standards. Work collaboratively with team members to manage inventory, restock supplies, and support the achievement of daily sales goals.

Accurately operate the cash register to process cash, credit, and digital payments while maintaining a balanced drawer. Deliver excellent customer service by efficiently handling orders and responding to customer questions in a friendly, professional manner.
Operated various complex machines to diligently produce custom designed orders and maintained a well-organized workspace.
